{"tid":1241470,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"3M 加入制裁 華為 Mate X 推出有暗湧","createTime":"2019-06-18T17:08:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T19:21:55.000Z","uid":22675,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"09c9870e7e998b2f14144c6dca8b6a18105b182b","tid":1241470,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T17:08:25.000Z","msg":"Andrew<br />\n2019-06-14<br />\n華為首部摺疊屏幕機 Mate X 預計在 7 月推出，不過因為美國禁令的影響，可能會令新機的推出增添變化。雖然華為會使用他們自家的處理器，就算因為 Google 的關係而不能使用 Android 系統，但仍然可以使用自家研發的「鴻蒙」 系統來執行 Android 應用 (不過是否完全支援就另作別論) ，但原來 Mate X 的柔性 OLED 屏幕，所需要的 OCA 光學透明黏合劑，是由美國 3M 生產。而日前 3M 已宣佈停止為華為提供黏合劑產品，當中當然包括 OCA&hellip; 而在欠缺了 OCA 的情況下，可能會影響 Mate X 的產量，甚至會令新機無法如期推出。"},{"pid":"638ec56713c23590501f208dca10ba78910e408d","tid":1241470,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T11:42:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/2019/06/14/3m-%e5%8a%a0%e5%85%a5%e5%88%b6%e8%a3%81-%e8%8f%af%e7%82%ba-mate-x-%e6%8e%a8%e5%87%ba%e6%9c%89%e6%9a%97%e6%b9%a7/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pcmarket.com.hk%2F2019%2F06%2F14%2F3m-%25e5%258a%25a0%25e5%2585%25a5%25e5%2588%25b6%25e8%25a3%2581-%25e8%258f%25af%25e7%2582%25ba-mate-x-%25e6%258e%25a8%25e5%2587%25ba%25e6%259c%2589%25e6%259a%2597%25e6%25b9%25a7%2F&d=HhKtR2wUfRZLc9nBt5dK8C2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=347dc9aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/2019/06/14/3m-%e5%8a%a0%e5%85%a5%e5%88%b6%e8%a3%81-%e8%8f%af%e7%82%ba-mate-x-%e6%8e%a8%e5%87%ba%e6%9c%89%e6%9a%97%e6%b9%a7/</a>"},{"pid":"5b52fdad0e907df13b9d63c29667174983136f6b","tid":1241470,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T19:13:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a02b19aec59ed81489df1c7db5c662cb5a7e42b7","tid":1241470,"uid":52763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T19:21:55.000Z","msg":"是但啦，侵g20傾完就會解除華為"}]}